trans-unit.source: Represents an ordered collection of <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"></xref> child elements.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção ordenada de <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"> </xref> elementos subordinados.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel> base class uses a UIElementCollection to represent its collection of child elements.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel>classe base utiliza uma UIElementCollection para representar a sua coleção de elementos subordinados.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel>

trans-unit.source: Methods and properties defined by the UIElementCollection affect all objects derived from <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel> and define a common feature-set for the manipulation of <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel> child elements.
trans-unit.target: Métodos e propriedades definidas pelo UIElementCollection afetam todos os objetos derivados <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel>e definir um conjunto de funcionalidades para a manipulação de comuns <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel>elementos subordinados.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel>
